    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137480/extras/3ee8ee06e1396391c14b1897ca0a9bcf.poster.avif?t=1731862511\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137480/extras/3ee8ee06e1396391c14b1897ca0a9bcf.webm?t=1731862511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137480/extras/3ee8ee06e1396391c14b1897ca0a9bcf.mp4?t=1731862511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Guide P.O.L.L.I - the Procedural Operating Layered Linguistic Intelligence - through 100+ challenging puzzles.  In order to progress, your task is to transform all available spaces into a single color.  Additionally, you have the option to skip puzzles, undo actions, or reset a challenge at any point in the game - all for the small cost of <strong>Cookies</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137480/extras/4c5c7cc6dd9d4fb6f46bdeabac9f5d7b.poster.avif?t=1731862511\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137480/extras/4c5c7cc6dd9d4fb6f46bdeabac9f5d7b.webm?t=1731862511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137480/extras/4c5c7cc6dd9d4fb6f46bdeabac9f5d7b.mp4?t=1731862511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>However,  <i>&quot;The Scientist&quot;</i> and their diligent <i>&quot;Assistant&quot;</i> are keeping a watchful eye on every move you make.  If you find yourself running low on cookies you risk being deemed a <strong>failure</strong> and having the experiment restarted. So think strategically, plan your moves carefully, and don't let those cookies run out!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137480/extras/a5f231710365ec103582e75879327af7.poster.avif?t=1731862511\" width=600 height=62 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137480/extras/a5f231710365ec103582e75879327af7.webm?t=1731862511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2137480/extras/a5f231710365ec103582e75879327af7.mp4?t=1731862511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>100+ Challenging Puzzles<br></li><li>Unlimited Undos [Technically]<br></li><li>Cookies!</li></ul>",
